Lead underwriter Muller and Co Incsaid an initial public offering of 500,000 units of &lt;AdvancedMarketing Technology Corp> is under way at eight dlrs a unit.    Each unit consists of four common shares and one Class Awarrant allowing the purchase of one common share and one ClassB warrant from March 25, 1987 until March 18, 1992.    Each Class B warrant will allow the holder to buy onecommon share at 2.80 dlrs during the same period. Reuter&#3;